title: Jake Bugg Triple J Rebroadcast 12.AUG.2013 45 Min Set Spledour i
description:
Triple J partly rebroadcast of Jake's set at Splendour in the Grass 2013.

On the weekend of Splendour Triple J broadcast a 20 mins version (the last 5 songs) which included the Neil Young cover, My My, Hey Hey. The rebroadcast was missing this song. It has been reinserted in the correct location, however the cuts don't match exactly...but it's worth having as it a great cover. 

The setlist:  

Kentucky
Trouble Town
Seen It All
Simple as This
Me and You
Slumville Sunrise
Ballad of Mr Jones
Broken
Two Fingers
Taste It
My My, Hey Hey (Out of the Blue) (Inserted from original broadcast)
Lightning Bolt

Enjoy....
